# Format Reference

A runnable tour of every waxon syntax extension.

<!-- note: Each slide that follows demonstrates one feature. Serve this deck to see it rendered. -->

--- #inline-color

# Inline Color

We grew revenue by .green{42%} while cutting churn to .red{1.2%}.

The .yellow{warning} signals bubble up through .blue{auth} and .aqua{cache} layers.

Nested works: .red{critical .yellow{warning} issue}.

Unknown classes like `.error{foo}` stay literal.

<!-- ai: Palette is red / green / yellow / blue / aqua / dim — closed set -->

--- #line-color

# Full-Line Color

.red This entire line is a failure state.

.green All systems nominal.

.yellow Slow query detected — investigating.

.blue Cache hit ratio: 94%.

Line color only fires at the start of an unindented line followed by a space.

